{
  "eyebrow": "Agent Logic Map",
  "title": "Day 3 · File + Web tools",
  "subtitle": "这张图只放 Day 3 的核心变化：ToolContext、fs_safety、本地发现工具、Web 工具边界。",
  "diagrams": [
    {
      "id": "main-loop",
      "label": "Main loop",
      "title": "从 prompt 到文件 Observation 的主循环",
      "summary": "模型只提出 tool_use；ToolRegistry 通过 ToolContext 把 cwd、SkipPolicy、ReadFileState 交给工具，工具执行后把 tool_result blocks 写回 messages。",
      "defaultActiveNodeId": "ctx",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "prompt",
          "kind": "runtime",
          "label": "user prompt",
          "eyebrow": "input",
          "body": "入口文件在哪里？",
          "detail": "用户仍然只输入自然语言。CLI 解析 prompt 和 --cwd，但不会自己猜要读哪个文件。",
          "position": { "x": 0, "y": 70 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 0 }
        },
        {
          "id": "messages",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "messages",
          "eyebrow": "context",
          "body": "Anthropic content blocks",
          "detail": "messages 保存用户问题、assistant tool_use，以及 harness 回填的 user tool_result blocks。",
          "position": { "x": 300, "y": 70 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 0 }
        },
        {
          "id": "provider",
          "kind": "model",
          "label": "AnthropicProvider",
          "eyebrow": "provider",
          "body": "complete(messages, tools)",
          "detail": "provider 仍然只做协议适配，把 tools schema 发给模型，再把 tool_use content block 翻译成内部 ToolCall。",
          "position": { "x": 600, "y": 70 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 210 }
        },
        {
          "id": "model-response",
          "kind": "response",
          "label": "ModelResponse",
          "eyebrow": "tool_use",
          "body": "list_files / read_file",
          "detail": "模型返回的是请求：例如先 list_files，再 read_file pyproject.toml。模型没有直接访问文件系统。",
          "position": { "x": 900, "y": 70 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 210 }
        },
        {
          "id": "registry",
          "kind": "tool",
          "label": "ToolRegistry",
          "eyebrow": "harness",
          "body": "run(call, ctx)",
          "detail": "ToolRegistry 根据 ToolCall.name 路由到具体 Python 函数，并把同一个 ToolContext 传进去。",
          "position": { "x": 900, "y": 320 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 420 }
        },
        {
          "id": "ctx",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "ToolContext",
          "eyebrow": "runtime",
          "body": "cwd + SkipPolicy + ReadFileState",
          "detail": "这是 Day 3 的关键抽象：工具不摸全局状态，而是通过 ToolContext 拿 cwd、skip 规则和 read_state。",
          "position": { "x": 600, "y": 320 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 420 }
        },
        {
          "id": "local-tools",
          "kind": "tool",
          "label": "local file tools",
          "eyebrow": "tools",
          "body": "list / read / grep",
          "detail": "本地工具负责真正读目录、读文件、按名字找、按内容搜。每个工具都先服从 ToolContext 里的 cwd 和 skip policy。",
          "position": { "x": 300, "y": 320 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 630 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tool-result",
          "kind": "response",
          "label": "tool_result blocks",
          "eyebrow": "observation",
          "body": "bounded Observation",
          "detail": "Day 3 会把同一轮 assistant 里所有 tool_use 的结果打包进紧接着的一条 user message，避免 Anthropic API 拒绝。",
          "position": { "x": 300, "y": 540 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 630 }
        },
        {
          "id": "stdout",
          "kind": "output",
          "label": "stdout",
          "eyebrow": "terminal",
          "body": "tool_call / final",
          "detail": "终端只展示 trace：tool_call、observation、final。完整 messages 和 read_state 留在 harness 内存里。",
          "position": { "x": 0, "y": 540 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 840 }
        }
      ],
      "edges": [
        { "id": "prompt-messages", "source": "prompt", "target": "messages", "label": "wrap" },
